n\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Ambitions on Sleeve &amp; TGI Community<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/harmony.one\/research\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Bring Research &amp; Privacy to Production<\/a><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/harmony.one\/story\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Coinbase Shortlist, Acquisition w\/ Animoca<\/a><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Appendix<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<h4>Wave Financial is a diversified asset manager built to bridge the gap between institutional capital and the digital asset markets<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Index<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Select 20 Index + Digital Fund in Q1 2019 and BTC Income &amp; Growth Digital Fund in Q2 2019 launched<\/li><li>Roadmap contains 14 other digital security issuances within the next 24 months<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Fund<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Early-stage crypto hedge fund started by the Founder of Wavemaker Partners<\/li><li>Invests in both equity and tokens of early stage companies and cryptocurrencies<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Harmony: Solving the Quadrilemma<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1966\" height=\"1118\" src=\"https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bea9bb83ab5a87fdd6bf_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.36.01-AM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3801\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bea9bb83ab5a87fdd6bf_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.36.01-AM.jpg 1966w, https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bea9bb83ab5a87fdd6bf_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.36.01-AM-768x437.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bea9bb83ab5a87fdd6bf_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.36.01-AM-1536x873.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1966px) 100vw, 1966px\" \/><figcaption>Achieving scalability, security, and decentralization is not an impossibility but an expansion of the triangle through great engineering. We add privacy, the fourth critical dimension.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Decentralization: Origin of 1,000+ Nodes<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>80% nodes by community<\/li><li>56% first-time operators<\/li><li>56% first-time operators<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1806\" height=\"972\" src=\"https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9beea519095d403260aa8_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.37.19-AM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3802\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9beea519095d403260aa8_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.37.19-AM.jpg 1806w, https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9beea519095d403260aa8_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.37.19-AM-768x413.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9beea519095d403260aa8_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.37.19-AM-1536x827.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1806px) 100vw, 1806px\" \/><figcaption>Harmony\u2019s program, Pangaea, onboards hundreds to run a network node for the first time.Consensus is meaningless without participation; tools are the most powerful equalizer.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>Quadratic Voting vs Capped Median<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Cap #stakers to network seats<\/li><li>Median decides effective stake<\/li><li>15% cap on top stakers from overtake, bottom from apathy<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1968\" height=\"848\" src=\"https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bf4dbb83abd752fdda21_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.38.55-AM.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3803\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bf4dbb83abd752fdda21_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.38.55-AM.png 1968w, https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bf4dbb83abd752fdda21_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.38.55-AM-768x331.png 768w, https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bf4dbb83abd752fdda21_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.38.55-AM-1536x662.png 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1968px) 100vw, 1968px\" \/><figcaption>Harmony presents a new staking scheme called Effective Proof-of-Stake, preventing top stakersfrom overtaking the network; and boost bottom stakers out of voter apathy.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>O(1) Secure Resharding<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>O(n2) view change, blocks in 1.3s<\/li><li>O(n2) view change, blocks in 1.3s<\/li><li>Verifiable Delay Function from scratch<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1548\" height=\"1020\" src=\"https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bfab4b9e5a93f1a1e552_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.40.31-AM.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3804\" srcset=\"https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bfab4b9e5a93f1a1e552_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.40.31-AM.jpg 1548w, https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bfab4b9e5a93f1a1e552_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.40.31-AM-768x506.jpg 768w, https:\/\/wavegp.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/11\/5de9bfab4b9e5a93f1a1e552_Screen-Shot-2019-12-06-at-10.40.31-AM-1536x1012.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1548px) 100vw, 1548px\" \/><figcaption>Harmony is among the first production mainnets with Proof-of-Stake and sharding. We productionize state-of-the-art research and implement from scratch the verifiable delay functions (VDF).<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4>The DeFi Stack: Lending Counterparties<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Speculating \/ hedging<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gaining additional exposure to a digital asset with leverage, shorting when you believe one may be overvalued<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u200d<strong>\u200d<\/strong><\/p>\n